Dialogue: 5,0:02:08.25,0:02:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Whenever he drank, my father would tell me this story.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:13.89,0:02:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder how many years it's been now.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:16.21,0:02:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One evening, on his way home from a neighboring village,
Dialogue: 5,0:02:19.40,0:02:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}he found himself lost.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:25.37,0:02:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He walked and walked until he lost sight of the road,{at first he was just lost, but then he walked around in circles until he wasn't even on a path/road any more}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:29.06,0:02:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but just when he was at a complete loss...
Dialogue: 5,0:02:34.11,0:02:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:35.99,0:02:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:37.60,0:02:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's where the road must be.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:42.49,0:02:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I wonder where that light is coming from.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.46,0:02:56.38,Mushisode Title,,0,0,0,eptitle,{\fad(2000,0)\an7\bord0\blur0.6\p1\c&H567520&\pos(-2,68)\fscx770\fscy90}m 0 0 l 100 0 100 100 0 100
Dialogue: 2,0:02:50.46,0:02:56.38,Mushisode Title,,0,0,0,eptitle,{\an4\fad(2000,0)\blur0.6\pos(3,109)}The Banquet at the Edge of the Forest
Dialogue: 5,0:02:57.41,0:02:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As he drew closer,
Dialogue: 5,0:02:58.78,0:03:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}an indescribably alluring scent of sake wafted toward him.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:04.33,0:03:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With that scent compelling him to sit down and take a sip,
Dialogue: 5,0:03:08.32,0:03:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}he snuck into the gathering to do just so.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:17.61,0:03:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The sake he'd smelled \Ngleamed like pure gold.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:41.77,0:03:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Rokusuke.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:42.78,0:03:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm over here!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:45.00,0:03:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You've done a fine job.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:48.51,0:03:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You can head home for the day and relax.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:51.96,0:03:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:54.03,0:03:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, um, Brewmaster?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:56.10,0:03:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:58.07,0:04:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering if I might take home a bit of this year's sake.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:02.83,0:04:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, of course.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:04.86,0:04:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm certain your father will be impressed this year.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:21.11,0:04:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When I was young, whenever Dad brewed sake,
Dialogue: 5,0:04:25.23,0:04:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'd have to take it to the neighboring village, \Nmuch like I'm doing now.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:32.41,0:04:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}During those times,
Dialogue: 5,0:04:35.07,0:04:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the moment I stepped onto the mountain path,
Dialogue: 5,0:04:36.74,0:04:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I felt like there were things clinging to me everywhere.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:41.47,0:04:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{Whoa!}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:42.11,0:04:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:45.47,0:04:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Phew, that was close.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:51.19,0:04:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}By the time I finally reached the village,{he says "errand destination", so he's talking about the place he was supposed to deliver the booze to}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:55.95,0:04:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}there was always noticeably less sake.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:01.73,0:05:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The brewmaster confronted me about it one day and scolded me rather harshly,
Dialogue: 5,0:05:08.45,0:05:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but my father never once reproached me because of it.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:13.87,0:05:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,When you were in the mountains, \Ndid it feel like something was clinging to you?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:18.63,0:05:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It did! There was stuff all around me that I couldn't see,
Dialogue: 5,0:05:22.85,0:05:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and before I knew it, some of the sake had disappeared.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:25.94,0:05:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Really!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:28.80,0:05:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:30.77,0:05:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Those things that clung to you love good sake.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:34.15,0:05:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,They must have found our brew \Nto be to their liking again this year.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:40.15,0:05:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But even tasting {\i1}this{\i0} good, it's still a far cry from that golden sake.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:45.67,0:05:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Golden sake?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:48.25,0:05:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I've told you about it before, haven't I?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:51.65,0:05:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That shining, golden sake...
Dialogue: 5,0:05:55.57,0:05:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never forget how it tasted.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:59.71,0:06:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been trying to get my sake to taste like that ever since.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:04.53,0:06:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Sake is a living thing, you know.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:07.15,0:06:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If I open up my senses and listen to what it's saying,
Dialogue: 5,0:06:12.02,0:06:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm certain it'll respond to me someday.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:16.09,0:06:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Sake can speak?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:17.69,0:06:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:19.29,0:06:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,If you intend to brew sake yourself one day, \Nbe sure to remember that.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:35.55,0:06:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've finally done it, Dad.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:47.11,0:06:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's perfect!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:59.37,0:07:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:02.57,0:07:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm tripping all over myself, for some reason.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:05.19,0:07:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I drunk already?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:09.51,0:07:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:11.07,0:07:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:13.73,0:07:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I must've taken a wrong turn somewhere.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:16.51,0:07:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I should {backtrack}retrace my steps.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:21.39,0:07:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:23.63,0:07:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this? Are these hairs from a wild animal?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:29.40,0:07:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{Oh!}
Dialogue: 5,0:07:30.75,0:07:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Wai—
Dialogue: 5,0:07:31.99,0:07:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:34.91,0:07:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:36.17,0:07:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, where are you taking it?!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:43.07,0:07:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back here.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:44.74,0:07:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me that!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:51.99,0:07:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I wonder where that light's coming from.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:59.71,0:08:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why are they in a place like this?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:04.83,0:08:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:07.19,0:08:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, well...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:14.93,0:08:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you have kouki.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:17.40,0:08:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,No need for you to be shy, then.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:29.61,0:08:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The sake's shining.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:33.41,0:08:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Does that mean this is...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:36.91,0:08:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the sake Dad told me about?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:40.79,0:08:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember ever meeting you before.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:42.48,0:08:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You a new mushi-shi?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:43.72,0:08:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:44.46,0:08:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:45.49,0:08:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So they'll go away if I give them some sake?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:03.09,0:09:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Mushi-shi"? Is that what these people are?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:28.10,0:09:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ginko.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:29.50,0:09:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got some good mushi cigarettes this time.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:31.52,0:09:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't say.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:33.59,0:09:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Want a few in exchange for some kouki?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:35.81,0:09:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What, are you out?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:38.29,0:09:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have much left myself, though.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:40.44,0:09:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:41.50,0:09:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you can spare at least a drop!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:44.47,0:09:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, then... in exchange for {\i1}all{\i0} your cigarettes.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:46.88,0:09:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:48.17,0:09:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that a bit too much?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:50.10,0:09:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, {\i1}you're{\i0} the one who ran out of kouki.{so you've only got yourself to blame}
Dialogue: 5,0:09:51.88,0:09:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, man, don't be like that.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:54.48,0:09:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{Oh!}
Dialogue: 5,0:09:55.00,0:09:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:58.89,0:10:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. I'm talking to you.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:00.98,0:10:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's kouki you've got in there, isn't it?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:02.66,0:10:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you spread the love a little?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:04.67,0:10:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, this is...
Dialogue: 5,0:10:06.54,0:10:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That jug looks nice and heavy.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:08.69,0:10:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit being so stingy.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:11.06,0:10:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're not interested in mushi cigarettes, I've got other goods too.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:19.95,0:10:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This cup looks so familiar.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:22.20,0:10:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that caught your eye?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:23.95,0:10:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I was told that it's a very famous piece.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:26.98,0:10:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I traded a cup of kouki for it back in the day.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:30.31,0:10:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got quite the eye, young man.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:33.05,0:10:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You forgot to mention that when you tried to pawn it, you found out it was a piece of junk.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:36.47,0:10:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You jerk!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:37.54,0:10:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This belonged to Dad.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:37.54,0:10:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Come on, Ginko!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:38.64,0:10:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Why don't you just shut your trap?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:39.15,0:10:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dad used to carry this around everywhere.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:41.22,0:10:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}What gives you the right to interfere in my business?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:44.03,0:10:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I have this?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:45.47,0:10:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You'll give me some kouki for {\i1}that{\i0}?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:48.14,0:10:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:48.80,0:10:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, can't say I have a problem with that.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:53.98,0:10:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks a lot.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:55.58,0:10:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:57.65,0:10:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's not going to drink it?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:00.23,0:11:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Actually, now that I notice it,
Dialogue: 5,0:11:01.95,0:11:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}not one person here is drinking the shining sake.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:05.25,0:11:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What in the world could it be for?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:10.29,0:11:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, Watari's crew is running a bit late, huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:12.76,0:11:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:13.91,0:11:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems they're having trouble getting things ready.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:17.20,0:11:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Getting what ready?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:18.44,0:11:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Again?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:20.65,0:11:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go take a look.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:24.35,0:11:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to come too...
Dialogue: 5,0:11:26.35,0:11:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey there, young man. \NYou sure have a lot of kouki there.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:29.50,0:11:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Care to share some with me as well?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:31.08,0:11:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and me too!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:32.66,0:11:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:45.47,0:11:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:47.01,0:11:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Isaza.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:48.28,0:11:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:49.01,0:11:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Ginko.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:50.99,0:11:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,How have you been?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:53.15,0:11:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Not bad, thank you.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:56.41,0:11:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We're about to get started.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:58.08,0:12:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We just decided on the location.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:01.53,0:12:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Having trouble finding a node of the River of Light again?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:06.39,0:12:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:08.40,0:12:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,This site is rather old, after all.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:11.51,0:12:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps next time, we'd be better off looking elsewhere.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:17.51,0:12:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Has it dried up?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:20.07,0:12:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's starting to dive deep underground.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:25.45,0:12:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm sure it will return once it's regained its strength.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:40.11,0:12:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's going on?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:41.41,0:12:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is something about to start?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:43.05,0:13:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's filled to the brim with shining sake now!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:46.71,0:13:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is this trickery?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:04.33,0:14:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, something's off.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:06.99,0:14:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Think that guy's a fake?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:09.40,0:14:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:10.73,0:14:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't me.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:13.28,0:14:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It was {\i1}him{\i0}!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:15.77,0:14:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I got that kouki from him.{this line is where he starts talking about the kouki}
Dialogue: 5,0:14:17.54,0:14:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the one who brought the fake kouki!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:19.91,0:14:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, get back here!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:21.54,0:14:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,After him!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:25.59,0:14:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What was {\i0}that{\i1} all about?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:28.53,0:14:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did I do something wrong?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:43.97,0:14:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've got to get out of here as fast as I can.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:47.61,0:14:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{Ah.}
Dialogue: 5,0:14:48.73,0:14:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! He's over—
Dialogue: 5,0:14:50.00,0:14:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, please!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:52.23,0:14:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't mean to do anything wrong.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:54.55,0:14:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,All I wanted was to try that shining sake.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:59.37,0:15:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry I pretended to be one of you to blend in.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:02.45,0:15:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:03.96,0:15:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're not a mushi-shi?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:06.38,0:15:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:07.50,0:15:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just a sake brewer from the {village at the }foot of this mountain.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:11.55,0:15:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,A brewer?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:13.19,0:15:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Then that sake you're holding is...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:15.35,0:15:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the sake we made this year.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:18.83,0:15:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It took years of trial and error before we managed to make this.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:23.98,0:15:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I was passing through, taking some home to my sick father so he could try it.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:28.26,0:15:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But then I got lost and somehow found all of you. That's all.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:32.35,0:15:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Please just let me go!{231}
Dialogue: 5,0:15:35.81,0:15:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,How exactly did you make that sake?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:39.99,0:15:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,After my father, the former brewmaster, collapsed,
Dialogue: 5,0:15:42.46,0:15:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,our sake lost its flavor.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:47.31,0:15:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Although I made sure I brewed the sake just like he used to,{he mentions he was following instructions here, and not just trying to mimic from memory}
Dialogue: 5,0:15:50.57,0:15:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I soon learned I also needed more time and experience to even come close to him.{he realised that he lacked the years of experience that his father had, and that he wouldn't be able to catch up that easily}
Dialogue: 5,0:15:54.99,0:15:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Nevertheless, I wanted to maintain our brewery's image,
Dialogue: 5,0:15:58.48,0:16:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,so I tried changing the rice, the water...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:01.21,0:16:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried everything I could think of, but nothing worked.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:04.65,0:16:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, one day, I had an idea.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:07.23,0:16:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I wondered what would happen if I tried changing the yeast.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:12.23,0:16:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So although our brewery had always used whatever yeast we had on hand,{always been using in-house yeast, or something? he's talking about how they just used stuff that lying in the warehouse}
Dialogue: 5,0:16:15.69,0:16:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I decided to try wild yeast for the first time.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:19.83,0:16:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Since yeast feeds on sugar,
Dialogue: 5,0:16:22.16,0:16:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I went around collecting yeasts from the nectars of different flowers.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:26.35,0:16:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I cultured and then used them,
Dialogue: 5,0:16:28.93,0:16:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,but most had no significant effect on the sake.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:32.67,0:16:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,However, one of the barrels was different.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:38.31,0:16:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Its yeast produced a beautiful sake with a golden glow.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:45.17,0:16:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So it was from nectar.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:47.67,0:16:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And drinking that sake didn't cause any odd side effects?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:51.25,0:16:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't drink much of it, so I can't say for sure,
Dialogue: 5,0:16:54.15,0:16:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,but I suppose it {\i1}did{\i0} make me feel strange.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:56.46,0:16:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I had an odd hallucination where I saw these dark red hairs everywhere.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:59.55,0:17:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That was no hallucination.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:01.87,0:17:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a Shoujounohige, \Nor "Drinker's Beard" mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.20,0:17:11.21,MushiNext,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&H626E6F&\fscx71\fscy71\frz348\fax-0.46\move(794,543,794,431,28,6993)\alpha&H80&}S{*\c&H616D6E&}ho{*\c&H606C6D&}ujo{*\c&H5F6B6C&}un{*\c&H5F6A6B&}o{*\c&H5E6A6B&}hi{*\c&H5E696A&}g{*\c&H5D696A&}e \N{*\c&H5C6869&}({*\c&H5C6768&}D{*\c&H5B6768&}ri{*\c&H5B6667&}n{*\c&H5A6667&}k{*\c&H5A6566&}er{*\c&H596566&}'{*\c&H596465&}s {*\c&H586364&}Bea{*\c&H576263&}rd{\c&H576263&})\h\h\h\h\h
